{"tid":2046093,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"聽住呀美國！陳茂波：聯繫匯率制度毋須美國同意","createTime":"2020-06-01T07:48:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T14:28:19.000Z","uid":156652,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e743af75c301538e9435efd53d4c7ffcb5474816","tid":2046093,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T07:48:09.000Z","msg":"【#時事第一手】 <br />\n<br />\n財政司司長陳茂波今早出席財經事務委員會會議時指出，根據《基本法》第112條，香港不會實行外匯管制措施，重申會保障資金流動，資金可自由進出，而金管局及銀行亦表示過去一個多星期未見明顯的資金外流。<br />\n<br />\n他又強調：「推行聯繫匯率制度毋須獲美國同意，最重要是香港有足夠的實力去實踐承諾，現時香港外匯儲備規模達4,400億美元，相當於基礎貨幣兩倍以上，而且銀行體系健康，資產質素高。」<br />\n-----------------------------------------------<br />\n緊貼財經即時資訊：<a href=\"https://www.capital-hk.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.capital-hk.com%2F&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns85uyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=f10d7d8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.capital-hk.com/</a> <br />\n#CapitalHK #資本平台 #陳茂波 #聯繫匯率"},{"pid":"671f2f62c6e7ee2b9b28e159b74209c665d60936","tid":2046093,"uid":260744,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T08:02:00.000Z","msg":"真係有咁多錢，冇俾中共偷到就係"},{"pid":"e0ae255eca2b25de7f07d470436550f84feb1144","tid":2046093,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T13:03:47.000Z","msg":"哭撚左[/b]"},{"pid":"ca68026647448611546227c77d105399f535a23a","tid":2046093,"uid":36378,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T13:04:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5df6707bbb9e8ee89c7b802753f9b177387337b","tid":2046093,"uid":295442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T14:28:19.000Z","msg":"佢有冇諗過李超人所有friends轉哂走㗎？<br />\n銀行水乾，佢去頂？"}]}